									li Display utility classes
									li Spacing utility classes (margin and padding)
									li Position utility classes
									li Flex utility classes (check on https://getbootstrap.com/docs/4.1/utilities/flex/)
							li Removed some icon classes that are not used
							li Included some modules that are often used (check under src/_mixins). Some examples are shown below
					li
						strong JS
						ul
							li Removed Vue
							li Added some node modules that are often used (e.g. wurl, date-fns)
							li Gulp Notify is enabled by default
							li Included some modules that are often used (check under src/_mixins). Some examples are shown below

		.row.u-mbb8.u-mbb10-md
